room_title: Escape room "Camp Crystal Lake" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
room_address: 9440 San Mateo Blvd Suite K Albuquerque, NM 87113
room_description: Camp Crystal Lake is a place with a dark past: for severals years, a masked killer terrorized the locals, but the trail always grew cold and the police were never able to catch him. Sent here to make sure the grounds are safe for the grand reopening, you find yourselves locked in a secluded cabin. Do you think you have what it takes to make it out alive?
